3.2.0-rc3 - 2024/04/03
- Added Allow ignoring ACL permissions
- Support CloudFront Signed Cookies
- Removed support for PHP versions older than 7.2.5

3.1.2 - 2023/12/12
- Update dependencies

3.1.1 - 2023/1/27
- More support for PHP 8 Compatibility support
- Update styles for bootstrap 5
- Remove unnecessory vendor files
- Enable option for cache control
- Support for version 9 (minimum version is now 8.5.6)

3.0.3 - 2018/9/14
- Update dependencies for PHP 7.2 support

3.0.2 - 2017/2/15
- Add support for IAM roles

3.0.1 - 2017/1/18
- Support for v8.1 (thumbnails and removes legacy autoloader)

3.0 - 2016/5/1
- Support for v8 (does not work on v5.7)

2.0.2 - 2015/12/27
- Added support for arbitrary hosts (Thanks Hissy)

2.0.1 - 2015/7/17
- Fixed support for 5.7.5
- Updated dependencies

2.0 - 2015/4/15
- Fixed support for 5.7.4
- Added the ability to specify region
- Added the ability to make urls expire

1.0
- Initial Release
